    <body>
        <p>
Choose a method to filter search results:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="userinput">First Matching Record</span>: returns the first record that matches.
            </li>
            <li><span class="userinput">First 200 Matching Records</span>: returns the first 200 matching records.
            </li>
            <li><span class="userinput">Stream Matching Records</span>: passes all matching records from your parent flow to a helper flow.&#160;A <span class="uicontrol">Streaming</span> input section is added to the card from which you can select a helper flow for streaming and adding custom extensible fields.</li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</html>